&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;this won't affect user experience (if my mental model is correct), but 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;sites using the API may receive less info than expected - but that's 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;kinda the point.
