&gt;&gt; *WebKit*: Shipped/Shipping (
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://webkit.org/blog/15443/news-from-wwdc24-webkit-in-safari-18-beta"&gt;https://webkit.org/blog/15443/news-from-wwdc24-webkit-in-safari-18-beta&lt;/a&gt;)
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *Web developers*: Strongly positive
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *Other signals*: Shipped on Meta Quest, Initially added to Chrome for
&gt;&gt; HoloLens support
