&gt; Explainer
&gt;
&gt; Attribution Reporting with event-level reports 
&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WICG/attribution-reporting-api/blob/main/EVENT.md"&gt;https://github.com/WICG/attribution-reporting-api/blob/main/EVENT.md&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
