On Thursday, September 19, 2024 at 12:00:25 PM UTC-7 Chromestatus wrote:&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

&gt; Contact emails cbiesin...@chromium.org 
&gt;
&gt; Explainer &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/fedidcg/FedCM/issues/555"&gt;https://github.com/fedidcg/FedCM/issues/555&lt;/a&gt; 
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/fedidcg/FedCM/issues/556"&gt;https://github.com/fedidcg/FedCM/issues/556&lt;/a&gt; 
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/fedidcg/FedCM/issues/559"&gt;https://github.com/fedidcg/FedCM/issues/559&lt;/a&gt; 
