&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *WebKit*: No signal (
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/401"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/401&lt;/a&gt;)
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *Web developers*: Positive (
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/web-platform-tests/interop/issues/726"&gt;https://github.com/web-platform-tests/interop/issues/726&lt;/a&gt;) An author
&gt;&gt; requested this to be part of Interop2025. Lots of +1 on the chrome bug.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *Other signals*:
&gt;&gt;
